Commentary: Mohammad Shami starts off with a fullish delivery but serves it wide outside the off stump. David Warner is watchful and leaves this one alone. Not much carry to the keeper.

David Warner and Australia are off and running! Mohammad Shami bowls this back of a length and outside the off stump. David Warner gets on his toes and dabs this towards covers with soft hands. They take a quick single.
On a good length this time and just outside the off stump. Usman Khawaja shoulders his arms to this one as the ball stays low once again.
Mohammad Shami comes 'round the wicket and serves this at the stumps on a good length. Usman Khawaja clips this towards square leg and takes one to open his account.
Delivers this wide outside the off pole on a shorter length. David Warner raises his arms and leaves the ball alone.
Continues to bowl on the outside off-stump channel. David Warner will let the ball go through to the keeper once again.

OUT! A huge wicket for India as the in-form Usman Khawaja has to depart! Mohammed Siraj draws first blood on his very first delivery and India are off to a good start! Massive shout! Mohammed Siraj bowls this full, on a leg stump line and gets the ball to shape back in. Usman Khawaja looks to clip this away but misses the line of the ball and plays all over this. A huge appeal from the Indian players around the bat. The umpire remains unmoved and after a delayed discussion Rohit Sharma goes upstairs for the review. UltraEdge shows there is no bat involved and Ball tracking shows three reds. The onfield decision has to be reversed and Australia lose their first wicket.
On a good length outside off, Marnus Labuschagne shoulders arms and leaves the ball alone.
Bowls this on a good length and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne leaves this one alone as the ball stays low once again.
Continues to bowl on a good length and well outside off. Marnus Labuschagne shoulders his arms to this one as well.
Beaten! That is a good delivery as he gets it closer to the off pole on a good length. Marnus Labuschagne feels for this one and the ball skims past the outside edge.
Offers width outside off once again on a good length. Marnus Labuschagne continues to raise his arm and leave the ball alone. A maiden wicket for Mohammed Siraj to start proceedings.

OUT! TIMBER! Mohammad Shami sends the stumps for a walk and both the Australian openers are back in the shed! Mohammad Shami bowls from 'round the wicket and serves this on a good length, angled into the stumps from outside off. David Warner gets forward slightly but plays the wrong line as the ball goes into the gap between the bat and the pad to send the off pole cart-wheeling away. Mohammad Shami and the Indian players look pumped up and this is just the start they were looking for. Australia are in a spot of bother here.

FOUR BYES! Mohammad Shami bowls this full and strays down leg. There is some late moevement in the air and the ball keeps going away from Srikar Bharat as he dives to his left. Four extra runs for Australia .
Shami serves this one fuller and swinging away outside off, Steven Smith does not reach out to the delivery and leaves it alone.
There is definitely some wing on offer here! Mohammad Shami bowls this wide outside the off stump on a good length. Steven Smith leaves this one alone as well.
On a good length and angling into the batter, Steven Smith shuffles a bit to work it on the leg side. The ball keeps a bit low but Smith still manages to push it to mid-wicket.
Bowls this on a good length as well and just outside the off pole. Steven Smith blocks this towards the mid on fielder. A maiden wicket for Mohammad Shami as well with just four byes conceded.

FOUR! That is a controlled shot from Marnus Labuschagne as Australia get their first boundary off the bat! Mohammed Siraj bowls this full and in line with the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne punches this straight towards long on for four runs.
Bowls on a good length this time and outside the off pole. Marnus Labuschagne dabs this towards the point fielder.
Continues to bowl on a good length and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne taps this into the pitch on the off side.

FOUR! Second boundary of the over and a bit of fortune in this one! Mohammed Siraj goes slightly fuller and outside the off pole. Marnus Labuschagne pushes at the ball and it takes the outside edge as it goes through the gap in the slip cordon for four runs to third man.
Goes back to bowling on a good length and outside off. Marnus Labuschagne raises his arms to this one.

What a jaffa! Mohammed Siraj bowls this on a good length and angles it into the batter but gets the ball to straighten after pitching. Marnus Labuschagne plays for the line of the ball and gets beaten on the outside edge,
Mohammad Shami strays onto the pads on a fuller length. Steven Smith clips this towards deep backward square leg and collects a couple of runs to get off the mark.
Bowls this one wide outside the off pole on a good length. Steven Smith not interested to play at this one.

FOUR! First boundary for Steven Smith and it is a beautiful cover-drive! Mohammad Shami bowls this slightly fuller and outside the off stump. Steven Smith gets a good stride forward and strokes this towards deep cover for four runs.
On a good length once again and outside the off stump. Steven Smith lets the keeper collect this one.
A tad bit fuller and outside the off pole. Steven Smith steps across the line of the stumps and looks to play at the ball but decides to leave it at the last moment.
Gets this one to nip back in sharply from a fuller length and just outside the off pole. Steven Smith is across the stumps once again but he just about manages to block this towards mid on.

FOUR! Another outside edge and four more runs added to Marnus Labuschagne's kitty! Mohammed Siraj bowls this full and in line with the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne looks to block this with soft hands but gets a thick edge that flies into the gap towards third man for four runs.
Bowls this on a good length and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne blocks this one out solidly.
Goes full and angles this into the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne dabs this towards the mid-wicket fielder.
Attacks the stumps once again on a good length. Marnus Labuschagne defends this back towards the bowler.

Bowls this one short and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne pulls this towards mid-wicket and Ravindra Jadeja makes a good stop low to his left. They take a single as the ball is parried towards mid on.
Bowls an in-swinger once again from a good length and just outside off. Steven Smith blocks this out towards the mid on fielder.
Ravindra Jadeja gets turn straight away! Bowls this full and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne pushes at the ball and gets beaten in the outside edge.
Floats this one full and in line with the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne blocks this towards mid on.
Bowls this one slightly short and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne dabs this towards point.
Angles this one into the stumps on a fuller length. Marnus Labuschagne defends this into the off side.
Tosses this one full as well and in line with the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne blocks this back down the pitch towards the bowler.
Strays onto the pads on a fuller length. Marnus Labuschagne misses his flick and the ball goes off the pads to the right of short fine leg for a leg bye. Ravindra Jadeja starts with a maiden.
Axar Patel begins with a shortish delivery bowled outside off. Marnus Labuschagne taps this towoards point.
Continues to bowl short and into the pads. Marnus Labuschagne clips this towards the mid-wicket fielder.
Bowls this one quick and into the stumps on a shorter length. Marnus Labuschagne tucks this towards square leg.
Flights this one full and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne blocks this towards short cover.
Bowls this one in line with the stumps on a fuller length. Marnus Labuschagne gets a stride forward and defends this back to the bowler.
Loopy delivery bowled full and on a leg stump line. Marnus Labuschagne makes rooms and knocks this straight to short cover.
Mohammed Siraj bowls a full delivery outside the off stump. Steven Smith blocks this to the left of the bowler.
Continues to bowl full and outside the off pole. Steven Smith gets across the stumps and defends this towards mid on.

Gets the ball to nip back in from a good length and outside off. Steven Smith steps across the stumps and looks to keep the ball out. Misses and gets hit on the pads. There is an inquiry from the bowler but the impact is clearly outside off.
Bowls this on a fuller length and outside the off stump. Steven Smith dabs this towards the cover fielder.

Continues to bowl full and just outside the off pole. Steven Smith knocks this back towards the bowler. Mohammed Siraj looks to grab the ball and throw it back but fumbles. He gives the batter the stare nonetheless.
Another fullish delivery bowled outside off. Steven Smith blocks this into the offside and indicates there is some extra bounce.
Axar Patel flights this full and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne drives this uppishly and the ball lands just short of cover.
Floats this one full as well and outside the off pole. Marnus Labuschagne knocks this straight to short cover.
Bowls this one short and into the pads. Marnus Labuschagne dabs this into the pitch on the leg side.
Loopy delivery bowled full and outside off. Marnus Labuschagne gets a good stride forward and blocks this towards silly point.
Another flighted delivery bowled full and outside off. Marnus Labuschagne pushes this into the vacant point region and takes a single.
Bowls this one slightly short and on an off-stump line. Steven Smith looks to stand tall and defend but gets squared up. The ball goes off the outside edge towards point.
Bowls this one back of a length and outside off, Marnus Labuschagne hangs back and dabs this one to cover.
Siraj pitches this one full and outside off, Marnus Labuschagne gets forward and drives it along the ground to mid off.
Full and angling in on middle by Mohammed Siraj, Marnus Labuschagne clips this one nicely but fails to get it past square leg.
On a good length around off, Marnus Labuschagne stays on the back foot and whips this one towards mid-wicket.
Full and angling into the batter from over the wicket, Marnus Labuschagne clips this one straight to mid-wicket.
Mohammed Siraj serves this one full and at the stumps, Marnus Labuschagne presents a straight bat and drives it to mid on. Another maiden for Mohammed Siraj.

Bye! Axar Patel floats this one full and outside off, the ball turns away after pitching, Steven Smith looks to drive it on the up but misses. Srikar Bharat behind the wicket misses as well and concedes a bye.
Darted in full and quicker on off, Marnus Labuschagne pushes this one from the crease to backward point.
Flighted, full around off, Marnus Labuschagne uses his feet and plays it towards Rohit Sharma at short cover.
Short and quicker at the stumps, the ball keeps a tad low but Marnus Labuschagne manages to block this one out.
Short and angling into the batter, Marnus Labuschagne stays on the back foot and defends it back to the bowler.
Tossed up, fuller on off, Marnus Labuschagne leans forward and steers this one wide of backward point and retains the strike with a single.
Shami starts with a full delivery on off, Marnus Labuschagne gets behind the line and drives it to mid on.
On a good length in the channel outside off, Marnus Labuschagne dabs this one to backward point.
Another delivery on a good length, Marnus Labuschagne pushes at the delivery away from his body but mishits it to mid-wicket.
Bowls this one fuller in length on the off stump, Marnus Labuschagne gets forward and works it to mid-wicket.
Serves this one fuller and outside off, a hint of away movement, Marnus Labuschagne drives this one from the toe end of the bat towards cover.
Good stop! On a length outside off, Marnus Labuschagne tries to steer this one through the slip cordon but Suryakumar Yadav stationed there at second slip makes a good diving stop to his right.
Floats this one full on off, Steven Smith pushes this one to short cover.
Another flighted delivery, full and outside off, Steven Smith gets forward to defend but gets an inside edge back onto his pads.
Short and angling at the pads, Steven Smith tries to defend on the back foot but gets an inside edge back onto his pads. The ball lobs towards the vacant short leg region.
Serves this one fuller in length on off, Steven Smith leans forward and defends it back to the bowler.
Bowls it full and on off, Steven Smith pushes this one from the front foot to short cover.
Short in length at the stumps, Steven Smith tries to use his feet and get to the pitch of the delivery but fails to do so. Ends up getting an inside edge back onto his pads.
Shami bowls this one fuller and angling down the leg side, Marnus Labuschagne tries to flick this one but misses.
On a length outside off, Marnus Labuschagne dabs this one along the ground to cover.
Another good-length delivery at the batter, Marnus Labuschagne tucks this one straight to mid-wicket.
Fuller and outside off, Marnus Labuschagne drives this one straight to backward point.

FOUR! Nicely played! Mohammad Shami bowls this one on a good length outside off, Marnus Labuschagne picks the length early and presses forward. Drives it along the ground and to the left of mid off for a boundary.
Fuller on off by Mohammad Shami, Marnus Labuschagne blocks this one out from the front foot.

DROPPED! Axar Patel bowls this one quicker and full outside off, Steven Smith frees his arms and slashes at the delivery. Gets an outside edge that flies quickly to the right of Virat Kohli at first slip. Kohli sticks out his right hand but the ball does not stick in his hand and Steven Smith gets a reprieve.
Fuller on off, Steven Smith gets forward and defends this one on the off side.
Floats this one full and outside the off stump. Steven Smith clocks this towards short cover.
Bowls this one short and outside off, much quicker through the air. Steven Smith punches this towards point.

This has shot up from the surface! Axar Patel flights this one full and outside the off pole. Steven Smith looks to get forward but is surprised by the extra bounce. Beats the outside edge as well and lobs up off the keeper's gloves. They take two byes in the process.
Flighted full and outside the off pole. Steven Smith blocks this towards short cover.
Ravindra Jadeja tosses this one full and outside off. Marnus Labuschagne knocks this towards mid off.
Flights this one full and into the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne gets forward and blocks this out.
Bowls this one short an outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne rocks back in the crease and blocks this into the off side.
Floats this one full and at the stumps, Marnus Labuschagne uses his feet and drives it wide of mid on for a single.
Full and drifting in on leg, Steven Smith gets behind the line and defends it back to the bowler.

FOUR! Ravindra Jadeja tosses this one full and on middle, Steven Smith shimmies down the track and gets to the pitch of the delivery. Lofts it over mid-wicket and collects a boundary. Good proactive batting by Steven Smith.
A polite enquiry but turned down! Axar Patel fires this one full and quicker on middle, Marnus Labuschagne gets forward to defend but gets an inside edge.
Short and angling in on middle and leg, Marnus Labuschagne looks to defend this one but gets hit high on the pads.
Fired in short and quicker at the batter, Marnus Labuschagne goes on the back foot and just about manages to keep the ball out.

FOUR! Fine shot from Marnus Labuschagne as he plays this really late! Axar Patel bowls this one slightly short and angles it into the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne goes deep in the crease and cuts this towards deep backward square leg for four runs.
Loopy delivery bowled into the pads. Marnus Labuschagne looks to block and gets an inside edge towards short leg.
Tossed up, fuller around off, Marnus Labuschagne gets forward and pushes it to backward point.
Starts with a flighted delivery, full on off, Steven Smith gets on the front foot and defends it to short cover.
Another full delivery on middle, Steven Smith gets behind the line and defends it down the wicket.
Fuller and at the stumps, Steven Smith leans forward and pushes it back to the bowler.
Short and on middle, Steven Smith goes back and defends it on the off side.
Full and angling in on middle and leg by Ravindra Jadeja, Steven Smith blocks this one out from the front foot.
Another fuller deliivery around off, Steven Smith presses forward and defends it on the off side.
Short and drifitng in on leg, Marnus Labuschagne stays on the back foot and pushes it to mid-wicket.
Fuller outside off, Marnus Labuschagne gets forward and pushes this one to cover.
Short and quicker at the stumps, Marnus Labuschagne stays back in the crease and defends it towards backward point.

FOUR! Easy pickings! Axar Patel strays on the pads and bowls it a bit short, Marnus Labuschagne rocks back on the back foot and flicks this one through square leg. Gets it wide of the man there and collects a boundary.
Floats this one full and into the pads. Marnus Labuschagne blocks this into the leg side.
A tad bit shorter and outside the off pole. Marnus Labuschagne knocks this towards extra cover.
Ravindra Jadeja bowls this short and outside off Steven Smith goes on the back foot and dabs this towards cover.
Goes full and into the pads. Steven Smith tucks this into the leg side.
Flights this one full and outside the off stump. Steven Smith shimmies down and blocks this towards short cover.
Goes full once again and outside off. Steven Smith dabs this towards the short cover fielder.
Gets this one to come back into stumps from a fuller length. Steven Smith pushes this towards point.
Massive turn there! Gets this to spin away from the bat on a fuller length. Steven Smith pushes at this outside off and gets beaten all ends up. Another maiden over for Ravindra Jadeja.
Ravichandran Ashwin starts from around the wicket and bowls this short just outside the off pole. Marnus Labuschagne looks to defend but gets an outside edge towards third man for a couple of runs.
Slightly short once again and in line with the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne tuck this towards short leg.
goes slightly fuller this time and straight. Marnus Labuschagne clips this towards mid-wicket.
Goes full and on the pads. Marnus Labuschagne taps this to the right of the short mid-wicket fielder.
Floats this one full and outside the off pole. Marnus Labuschagne blocks this back to the left of the bowler.
Some turn and bounce this time! Bowls this on a shorter length and on a leg stump line. Marnus Labuschagne looks to defend but misses and gets hit on the body.
Ravindra Jadeja flights this full and outside the off stump. Steven Smith dabs this towards cover.
How close was that! Ravindra Jadeja bowls a loopy delivery full and on an off stump line. The ball spins away from the bat and misses the off pole by a fraction.
Goes full once again and outside the off stump. Steven Smith defends this into the off side.
FOUR! That's a cracking shot! Ravindra Jadeja bowls this slightly short and outside off. Steven Smith rocks back and punches this to deep cover for four runs.
Floats this one full and outside the off pole Steven Smith defends this towards short cover.
Goes full once again and in line with the stumps. Steven Smith defends this back towards the bowler.
Ravichandran Ashwin bowls this short and on the pads. Marnus Labuschagne clips this towards deep square leg for a single.
Floats this one full and at the stumps. Steven Smith defends this back to the bowler.
Tossed up, full and at the stumps, Steven Smith advances down the track and clips it to deep mid-wicket for a single.
Bowls this short and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne guides this to backward point for a single.
Continues to bowl short and on a leg stump line. Steven Smith blocks this towards mid on.
This is outside the off pole on a shorter length. Steven Smith walks across the stumps and clips this to square leg.
Ravindra Jadeja floats this one full and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne dabs this towards point.
Bowls this in line with the stumps on a fuller length. Marnus Labuschagne gets forward and smothers the ball into the leg side.
Loopy delivery bowled full and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne strokes this firmly but straight to the cover fielder.
Tosses this full as well and closer to the off pole. Marnus Labuschagne gets a stride forward and blocks this to short cover.
Slightly shorter this time and outside off. Marnus Labuschagne goes on the back foot and keeps this one out.
Loopy delivery bowled full and into the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne shimmies down the wicket and clips this towards mid-wicket/ The fielder makes a good stop diving to his left.
Ashwin bowls this one short and turning in on middle, Steven Smith allows the ball to turn and defends it back to the bowler.
Flighted, fuller at the stumps, Steven Smith gets forward and clips it to the left of deep square leg for a single.
Full and on middle and leg, Marnus Labuschagne gets a stride forward and pushes it to short mid-wicket.
Tossed up, fuller outside off, Marnus Labuschagne tries to work it on the leg side but close the bat face early. Miscues it towards cover for a dot.
Short and turning into the batter, Marnus Labuschagne goes back in his crease and flicks it towards deep square leg for a single.
Full and quicker outside off, Steven Smith defends this one from the front foot towards cover.
Full and at the stumps by Ravindra Jadeja, Marnus Labuschagne stays inside the line and tries to sweep the delivery. But gets a bottom edge back onto his pads.
Beauty! Short and turning away outside off, Marnus Labuschagne goes back to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge by the sharp away turn.
Fuller on off, Marnus Labuschagne gets forward and strokes it to short cover.
Short and quicker on middle and leg, Marnus Labuschagne goes back and blocks this one out.
Floats this one full and just outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne gets a stride forward and blocks this into the off side.
Bowls this one full and on middle, Marnus Labuschagne presses forward and defends it down the wicket.
Serves this one full and around off, Steven Smith steps out and drives it firmly to mid on. They cross for a single.
Floats this one full outside off, Marnus Labuschagne presses forward and pushes it to mid on for a single.
Short and quicker outside off, Steven Smith advances down the track but can only block this one out towards extra cover.
Fuller in length outside off, Steven Smith gets forward and blocks this one out on the off side.
Tossed up, full around off, Steven Smith clips it firmly towards Rohit Sharma at short mid-wicket.
A bit short in length outside off, Steven Smith uses his feet and defends this one down the wicket.

FOUR! Beautiful timing! Ravindra Jadeja floats this one full and on middle and leg, Marnus Labuschagne leans forward and plays it against the turn. Drives this along the ground and gets it right between mid-wicket and mid on for a boundary.
Short and at the stumps, Marnus Labuschagne stays on the back foot and defneds it back to the bowler.
Fuller in length on middle, Marnus Labuschagne takes a stride forward and knocks it to mid on for a single.
Fuller around off by Ravindra Jadeja, Steven Smith clips it firmly towards mid-wicket but fails to get it past Cheteshwar Pujara.
Full and at the stumps, Steven Smith drives it firmly to the right of the bowler. Ravindra Jadeja reacts quickly and makes a good stop.
Darted in short and on leg, Steven Smith looks to defend but gets beaten on the inside edge and gets hit on the pads.

Ashwin tosses this one full and at the stumps, Marnus Labuschagne shimmies down the track and clears this front leg at the last moment to go inside out. Drives it through covers and batters run three there.
Fuller delivery on middle and leg, Steven Smith looks to turn this one on the leg side but gets an inside edge that falls wide of short leg.
Full and on middle and leg, Steven Smith drives this one towards mid on and takes a quick single.
Full and at the pads, Marnus Labuschagne blocks this one out from the front foot on the leg side.

FOUR! Smart batting! Flighted outside off by Ravichandran Ashwin, Marnus Labuschagne picks the length early and paddles this one wide of short fine leg. Mohammed Siraj does perform the chase but the ball had enough legs on it to reach the fence.
Fullish delivery at the stumps, Marnus Labuschagne works this one to mid on and retains the strike with a single.
Ravindra Jadeja fires this one full and into the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne knocks this back towards the bowler.
Angles this into the pads on a fuller length. Marnus Labuschagne dabs this towards mid-wicket.
Bowls this short and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne looks to punch this into the off side but gets an inside edge towards square leg.
Flights this one full and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne pushes this towards short cover.
Tosses this one full as well and outside off. Marnus Labuschagne strokes this to the fielder at cover-point.
Loopy delivery bowled on an off stump line. Marnus Labuschagne defends this to the left of the bowler.
Axar Patel bowls this short and outside the off stump. Steven Smith misses out as he mistimes his cut towards cover-point.
Floats this one full and into the off stump. Steven Smith blocks this back towards the bowler.
Flights this one full and outside the off pole. Steven Smith strokes this straight to cover-point.
Gets this one to skid into the stumps on a fuller length. Steven Smith gets his bat low and keeps the ball out.
Strays onto the pads this time on a shorter length. Steven Smith tucks this towards square leg for a single.
Tosses this one full and angles it into the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne gets his front foot forward and defends this towards mid on. That will be LUNCH on DAY 1!
Mohammad Shami starts off with a full delivery in line with the stumps. Steven Smith clips this towards short mid-wicket.
Continues to bowl full and just outside the off stump. Steven Smith blocks this towards mid off.
FOUR! Steven Smith slaps this away! Mohammad Shami bowls this short and outside off. Steven Smith swivels and pulls this towards deep square leg for four runs.
Goes full this time and angles this into the pads. Steven Smith clips this towards square leg and sets off for a single.

Goes full and angles this into the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne looks to clip this away but misses and gets hit on the pads. There is an appeal but the umpire remains unmoved. There is a discussion about whether to take the review and Rohit Sharma decides against it.
Bowls this on a good length and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne dabs this towards the cover fielder.
Ravindra Jadeja floats this one full and into the stumps. Steven Smith leans forward and defends this into the off side.
Flights this one full and outside the off stump. Steven Smith drives this wide of mid off and takes a single.
Skids this one into the stumps and on a fuller length. Marnus Labuschagne goes deep in the crease and gets his bat down in time. Taps the ball towards point.
Fires this one full and in line with the stumps. Marnus Labuschagne dabs this towards silly point.
Goes full and attacks the stumps once again. Marnus Labuschagne goes deep in the crease and punches this towards mid on.
Tosses this one full as well and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne pushes this wide of cover and takes one to retain strike.
Mohammad Shami bowls this really full and on an off-stump line Marnus Labuschagne digs this out towards mid on.

Australia doing it nicely here! There are being watchful and rotating the strike while at the same time putting bad balls away. This is full and on the pads. Marnus Labuschagne clips this towards deep square leg for a single.
Continues to bowl full and this time outside the off stump. Steven Smith dabs this towards cover.
Bowls this in line with the stumps on a fuller length. Steven Smith taps this back down the pitch.
Attacks the stumps once more and continues to bowl full. Steven Smith knocks this back towards the bowler.
Goes full once more and just outside the off pole. Steven Smith blocks this solidly back down the pitch.
Ravindra Jadeja bowls this full and on a leg stump line. Marnus Labuschagne dabs this into the leg side.
This is short and outside the off stump. Marnus Labuschagne pushes this towards point.
Flights this one full and outside off. Marnus Labuschagne stays in the crease and taps it into the off side.
Goes full this time and into the pads. Marnus Labuschagne smothers this inro the pitch on the front foot.

OUT! STUMPED! Ravindra Jadeja gets the breakthrough and that is great work behind the wicket by Srikar Bharat! The dangerous Marnus Labuschagne has to make the long walk back to the shed. Ravindra Jadeja flights this one full and on an off stump line. Marnus Labuschagne leans forward and looks to work this leg side and his back foot leaves the crease as his weight comes forward. The ball spins away from the bat and beats the outside edge. Srikar Bharat collects the ball in a flash and whips the bails off. The replays show the batter is well out of the crease and Australia lose their third wicket.
Howout: st Srikar Bharat b Ravindra Jadeja

Commentary: OUT! LBW! Ravindra Jadeja has two wickets in two balls and India have managed to claw themselves back on top! Ravindra Jadeja fights this one full and in line with the stumps. Matt Renshaw gets forward and looks to work this leg side but misses and gets hit on the pads. A huge appeal from all the Indian players around the bat and the umpire raises his finger. Matt Renshaw discusses it with Steven Smith and they decide to go for the review. There does not seem to be any bat involved and Ball Tracking shows umpire's call on wickets hitting so the onfield decision stays. Australia are four down all of a sudden and the Indians look elated. Ravindra Jadeja will be on a hat-trick on the first ball of his next over.
On a length outside off by Mohammad Shami, Steven Smith shuffles across and pushes this one to cover.
Fuller and outside off, Steven Smith moves across and steers this one to backward point. Axar Patel there does fumble but the batters decide not to run a single.
Goes full on the pads. Steven Smith clips this towards square leg.
Bowls this one full and outside the off stump. Steven Smith knocks this straight to cover.
Continues to bowl full and angles this into the stumps. Steven Smith clips this towards mid-wicket.

On a good length this time and outside the off pole. Steven Smith covers the line of the ball and taps this towards cover. Maiden over from Mohammad Shami to follow up the two wickets by Ravindra Jadeja.

NO BALL! Peter Handscomb safely negotiates the hat-trick ball! Ravindra Jadeja bowls this full and outside the off stump. Peter Handscomb dabs this towards silly point. He has overstepped though and the wicket would have not counted even if he had got one.
Flights this full and in line with the stumps. Peter Handscomb blocks this back towards the bowler.
Tosses this full as well and keeps it straight. Peter Handscomb looks to defend and gets an inside edge towards square leg.
Continues to bowl straight and on a fuller length. Peter Handscomb gets forward and taps it back down the pitch towards the bowler.
Jadeja bowls this one full and quicker at the stumps, Peter Handscomb gets forward and defends it back to the bowler.
Flighted, full and on middle, Peter Handscomb leans forward and smothers the ball on the off side.
Floats this one full and outside the off stump. Peter Handscomb defends this to the left of the bowler.
Mohammad Shami bowls this one a good length and on an off stump line. Steven Smith gets behind the ball and blocks this to mid on.
Goes really full this time and outside the off stump. Steven Smith digs this out towards mid on.
On a good length once again and outside the off pole. Steven Smith defends this solidly back towards the bowler.
Back to bowling full and angles this into the stumps from outside off. Steven Smith knocks this towards cover.
Attacks the stumps on a fuller length. Steven Smith flicks this towards mid-wicket.
Another maiden over for Mohammad Shami. This is bowled just outside the off pole on a good length. Steven Smith pushes this towards mid on.
Ravindra Jadeja bowls this full and in line with the stumps. Peter Handscomb dabs this just to the left of short leg.
FOUR! Great use of the crease here! Ravindra Jadeja bowls this one slightly short and outside off. Peter Handscomb goes back towards the stumps and cuts this towards deep point for four runs.
Loopy delivery bowled full and on a leg stump line. Peter Handscomb dabs this back down the pitch.
Tosses this one full as well on middle and leg. Peter Handscomb defends this to the right of the bowler.
Attacks the stumps once again on a fuller length. Peter Handscomb gets forward and taps this towards mid on.

FOUR RUNS! Ravindra Jadeja bowls this really quick and short, into the pads. Peter Handscomb rocks back and punches this towards deep mid-wicket. Ravichandran Ashwin gives chase and by the time he gets the ball back the batters run four runs.
FOUR! Cracking shot! Axar Patel floats this one full and outside off, Steven Smith gets the width he needs and he frees his arms. Thumps this one over covers and collects a boundary.
Full and quicker at the stumps, Steven Smith blocks this one to short cover.
FOUR! Tossed up, full and outside off, Steven Smith allows the ball to come to him and slices this one past backward point for a boundary. Steven Smith is looking to be positive here.
Flatter and quicker at the stumps, Steven Smith defends this one out on the off side.
Short and at the stumps, Steven Smith defends this one from the crease.

FOUR! Steven Smith has not let Axar Patel settle in this over and gets the third boundary! Axar Patel bowls this one full and outside off, right in the slot for the batter, Steven Smith picks the length early and lofts it over mid off for another boundary.
Ravindra Jadeja bowls this full and on the pads. Peter Handscomb flicks this towards deep backward square leg for a couple of runs.
Flights this one full and in line with the stumps. Peter Handscomb leans forward to defend, gets an inside edge towards square leg for a single.
Sharp turn! Full and quicker outside off, Steven Smith presses forward to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge by the away turn.
NO BALL! Short and angling into the pads, Steven Smith stays in the crease and works it to short fine leg.
Full and around off by Ravindra Jadeja, Steven Smith gets forward and defends it on the off side.
A bit fuller on off, Steven Smith prods forward but gets an outside edge. The edge does not carry to Virat Kohli at first slip.

OUT! CLEANED HIM UP! Steven Smith is perplexed but has to make his way back now. Ravindra Jadeja bowls this one on a length on the off stump, Steven Smith gets forward and plays for the turn. The ball goes through with the arm and beats Steven Smith all ends up. The ball sneaks through the gap between bat and pad and takes the off stump. Ravindra Jadeja gets his third wicket and Australia have half their side back in the hut.
Starts with a full toss on leg, Peter Handscomb clips this one straight to mid-wicket.
Bowls this short and just outside off. Peter Handscomb knocks this back towards the bowler.
Tossed up, full on middle, Peter Handscomb gets forward and defends it down the wicket.
FOUR! Put away by Peter Handscomb! Ravichandran Ashwin misses his length and bowls a full toss on middle, Peter Handscomb does not miss out and clips this one through mid-wicket for a boundary.
Flighted, full and outside off, Peter Handscomb pushes it towards cover and takes a single.

FOUR! Alex Carey is up and running! Ravichandran Ashwin bowls a fullish delivery on off, Alex Carey brings out the reverse sweep and executes it to perfection. Gets it to the right of short third man and opens his account with a boundary.
Full on off, Peter Handscomb leans forward and smothers the ball down the wicket.
Another full delivery on middle, Peter Handscomb gets behind the line and blocks this one out.
Keeps it full again and on middle, Peter Handscomb leans forward and defends it on the off side.

A loud appeal but turned down! Ravindra Jadeja angles this one full and around off, the ball spins away after pitching and beats Peter Handscomb on the outside edge. Jadeja thought he heard a noise and went up in appeal but it is turned down. Rohit Sharma decides not to send it upstairs.
NO BALL! Bowls this one full and on middle, Peter Handscomb watchfully blocks this one out back to the bowler. Ravindra Jadeja has overstepped and will have to bowl this one again.
Full and on off, Peter Handscomb drives it firmly back to the bowler.
Fired in full and at the pads, Peter Handscomb looks to help it fine but fails to get any bat on it.
Fuller around off, Alex Carey tries to defend this one but gets it from the inner part of the bat.
Tossed up, full at the stumps, Alex Carey defends this one from the front foot.
Fuller around off, Alex Carey gets forward and defends it on the off side.
Bowls this full and into the stumps. Alex Carey paddles this towards fine leg for a single.
Loops this full and just outside the off stump. Peter Handscomb defends this back towards the bowler.
Slightly short this time and outside the off pole. Peter Handscomb rocks back and dabs this into the leg side.

FOUR! Another reverse sweep reaps rewards for Alex Carey! Ravindra Jadeja bowls this one full and quicker on off, Alex Carey gets into the position early and reverse sweeps this one along the ground towards deep backward point for a boundary.
Flatter and quicker at the stumps, Alex Carey reverse sweeps it to deep backward point for a boundary.
Flighted, full on off, Peter Handscomb smothers the ball on the off side.
FOUR! Darted in full and quicker at the stumps, Peter Handscomb goes back in his crease and tries to push this one on the off side. Gets an outside edge that goes past first slip for a boundary.
Floated, full outside off, Peter Handscomb defends it to cover.
Full and around off, Peter Handscomb gets forward and blocks this one out.
Bowls this one full and on off, Alex Carey drives it straight to short cover.
Full and angling into the batter, Alex Carey reverse sweeps but fails to get it past backward point.
Full and quicker on off, Alex Carey gets forward to defend but gets an inside edge back onto his pads.
Flighted, full on off, Alex Carey smothers the ball to short cover.
Full and quicker on middle, Alex Carey goes for the reverse sweep again and gets it over backward point for a single.
Full and around off, Peter Handscomb leans forward to defend but gets it from the inner part of the bat towards square leg.
FOUR LEG BYES! Full and at the pads, Alex Carey tries to paddle this one but gets it off his pads. The ball goes past leg slip for a boundary.
Fullish delivery on off, Alex Carey reverse sweeps this one towards third man for a single.
Flighted, full at the batter, Peter Handscomb gets forward and defends it back to the bowler.
Fired in quicker, full on middle, Peter Handscomb blocks it to short cover.
Fuller and on off, Peter Handscomb leans forward and dabs it to point.
Another full delivery at the stumps, Peter Handscomb gets behind and plays it back to the bowler.
Full and angling at the stumps, Alex Carey presses forward and defends it to back to the bowler.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Alex Carey tries to defend but gets an inside edge towards square leg for a single.
Fuller around off, Peter Handscomb smothers the ball back to the bowler.
Loopy delivery, full on middle, Peter Handscomb clips it straight to mid-wicket.
Fullish delivery on middle, Peter Handscomb works this one towards short fine leg.
Flighted, full on off, Peter Handscomb blocks this one out down the wicket.
Siraj starts with a shortish delivery at the batter, Alex Carey hangs back and flicks it to square leg.
FOUR! On a good length outside off, Alex Carey lets his hands flow and goes through with the drive. Gets it through covers for a boundary.
Back of a length outside off from 'round the wicket, Alex Carey stays on the back foot and punches it to cover.
FOUR! SHOT! Mohammed Siraj pitches this one full and outside off, Alex Carey does not miss out as he leans into the drive and gets it past short cover for a boundary.
Siraj bowls this one on a good length outside off, Alex Carey pushes at the delivery but gets a fine tickle on it. Luckily for him, the ball does not carry to Srikar Bharat behind the wicket.
On a length outside off, Alex Carey defends this one on the off side.
Flighted, full on off, Peter Handscomb works this one towards the vacant covers region and collects a couple of runs.
Fuller outside off, Peter Handscomb gets forward and pushes it to cover for a single.
A bit short and at the pads, Alex Carey knocks it to mid on and takes a single.
Tosses this one full on off, Peter Handscomb clips it straight to mid-wicket.
Full and turning in on off, Peter Handscomb presses forward but can only push it back to the bowler.
Short and quicker at the stumps, Peter Handscomb goes back and pushes it back to Ravichandran Ashwin.
Full and quicker on off, Alex Carey reverse sweeps but fails to get it past first slip.
FOUR! Full and on off, Alex Carey picks the length early and uses the pace. Paddles this one through short fine leg for a boundary.
Full and angling away on off, Alex Carey reverse sweeps this one towards backward point.
Short and quicker outside off, Alex Carey guides this one awkwardly towards third man for a single.
Full and angling in on middle, Peter Handscomb smothers the ball on the leg side.
Slower and full on off, Peter Handscomb gets behind the line and watchfully blocks this one out.
FOUR! Alex Carey welcomes Siraj with a boundary! Mohammed Siraj bowls this one fuller and outside off, Alex Carey opens the bat face and slices this one towards third man for a boundary.

FOUR! Back-to-back boundaries for Alex Carey! This is even better! Shorter in length around off, Alex Carey lets the ball come to him and steers it through the slip cordon for a boundary. 50-run stand comes up.
Back of a length and angling away outside off from over the wicket, Alex Carey punches this one to cover.
Shorter in length and at the batter, Alex Carey goes for the pull but the ball keeps a bit low and he gets hit on the body.
Slower and on a length on leg, Alex Carey works this one towards square leg and takes a single.
Back of a length and angling in on middle and leg, Peter Handscomb works this one straight to mid-wicket.

OUT! BOWLED! Test wicket number 450 for Ravichandran Ashwin! The reverse sweep brings about the demise of Carey! Ashwin floats this one full and on leg from 'round the wicket, Alex Carey goes for the reverse sweep but does not execute it this time. Gets a bottom edge and the ball trickles back onto the stumps. Ravichandran Ashwin gets a much-needed breakthrough for India. Australia lose their sixth wicket as Alex Carey's counter-attacking cameo comes to an end.
Fuller and on off, Pat Cummins gets forward and defends it down the wicket.
FOUR! Ashwin tosses this one full and on off, Pat Cummins tries to defend this one but gets an outside edge that goes past first slip and gets off the mark with a boundary.
Short and on off, Pat Cummins looks to work it on the off side but gets an outside edge that goes past short third man for a couple of runs.
Fuller on off, Pat Cummins drives it firmly to mid off.
Short and on off, Pat Cummins goes back and defends it on the off side.
Bowls this one full and turning away outside off, Peter Handscomb presses forward to defend but gets an outside edge that goes on the bounce to first slip.
Full and at the stumps, Peter Handscomb smothers the ball to short cover.
Full and around off, Peter Handscomb presses forward and defends it on the off side.

Beauty! Ravindra Jadeja bowls this one quicker and fuller on off, the ball spins away after pitching and beats Peter Handscomb on the outside edge. There was a polite enquiry for stumping but the replays show that Peter Handscomb had his back leg grounded inside the crease.
Fired in full and off, Peter Handscomb defends it to short cover.

FOUR! DROPPED! Ravindra Jadeja bowls this one short and quicker on off, Peter Handscomb goes back in his crease to defend but gets an outside edge. The ball comes off Srikar Bharat's gloves behind the wicket and the deflection makes it tough for Virat Kohli to react at first slip. The ball runs towards the third man fence for a boundary.
Ravichandran Ashwin floats this one full and outside the off stump. Pat Cummins pushes this towards point.
Bowls this one an off stump line and on a shorter length. Pat Cummins blocks this down the pitch.
Goes full and outside the off stump. Pat Cummins knocks this back towards the bowler.
Loopy delivery bowled onto the pads. Pat Cummins dabs this into the leg side.
Tosses this one full and on a leg stump line. Pat Cummins defends this back towards the bowler.
Bowls this in line with the stumps on a fuller length. Pat Cummins goes deep in the crease and keeps the ball out. Maiden over from Ravichandran Ashwin.
Ravindra Jadeja floats this one full and just outside the off pole. Peter Handscomb pushes at this and gets beaten.
Goes full once again and in line with the stumps. Peter Handscomb blocks this towards mid on.
What a jaffa! Ravindra Jadeja flights this full and outside the off pole. Peter Handscomb leans into the shot and gets beaten by the turn.
Loopy delivery bowled full and outside the off stump. Peter Handscomb knocks this towards cover.
Slightly short and just outside the off pole. Peter Handscomb plays this late and dabs it down towards the slip fielder.
Angles this into the pads on a shorter length. Peter Handscomb rocks back and taps this towards mid-wicket.
Ravichandran Ashwin beats the inside edge of the bat! Floats this one full and outside the off stump. Pat Cummins looks to drive and gets beaten as the ball just shaves the off pole.
Loops this one full and outside the off stump. Pat Cummins dabs this towards the off side.

OUT! CAUGHT! Ravichandran Ashwin gets another one and this is really intelligent bowling from the Indian stalwart! After two off-spinning deliveries, he allows this one to go straight with the arm and serves this outside the off pole. Pat Cummins hangs his bat out to dry and gets an outside edge which goes to Virat Kohli at first slip. He makes no mistake holding onto the catch and Australia have lost their skipper. India have their seventh wicket and will be looking to wrap the innings up before the 200-run mark.
Howout: c Virat Kohli b Ravichandran Ashwin

Commentary: Great delivery first up! Bowls from 'round the wicket and delivers this full outside off. Todd Murphy pushes at this and gets beaten on the outside edge.
Goes full once again and outside the off stump. Todd Murphy look to defend and gets an outside edge just short of second slip to his right.
Floats this one full and outside the off stump. Todd Murphy defends this awkwardly into the off side.
Fuller outside off, Peter Handscomb presses forward and defends it to short cover.
Full and quicker outside off, Peter Handscomb defends this one back to the bowler.
Flights this full and outside the off stump. Peter Handscomb dabs this into the off side and takes a run.
Goes full and into the pads. Todd Murphy clips this towards mid-wicket.

OUT! PLUMB! Ravindra Jadeja is on a roll here and what a comeback this has been for him so far after his injury! He gets his fourth wicket and the debutant has to depart without troubling the scorers. Ravindra Jadeja bowls this full and in line with the stumps. Todd Murphy gets his front foot forward and looks to clip this leg side. There are two sounds as the ball balloons up and goes into the hands of slip. There is a loud appeal and the umpire raises his finger. The two batters get together and after some discussion decided to go upstairs. UltraEdge shows there is no bat involved as the second noise was the bat hitting the pad. The check Ball Tracking and it shows three reds so the onfield decision stays and Australia lose their eighth wicket.
Floats this one full and outside the off stump. Nathan Lyon blocks this into the off side.
Flights this one full and just outside the off stump. Peter Handscomb flicks this to wide mid on and refuses the single. He will keep strike for the last over of the session.
Tosses this one full and into the stumps. Peter Handscomb gets forward to defend this.
Flights this one full and outside the off pole. Peter Handscomb lunges forward to smother this into the off side.
Fuller outside off, Peter Handscomb pushes it towards the vacant cover region and takes a single.
Flighted, full and outside off, Nathan Lyon drives it back to the bowler.
Tosses this one full and outside the off pole. Nathan Lyon dabs this into the off side. The umpires call for TEA on Day 1
Starts with a flighted delivery, full on off, Peter Handscomb defends it back to the bowler.
Full and angling in on off, Peter Handscomb smothers the ball on the off side .
Slower and full on off, Peter Handscomb gets behind the line and blocks this one out.
Full and at the stumps, Peter Handscomb paddles this one straight to short fine leg.
Tossed up, full and outside off, Peter Handscomb tries to sweep from outside off but fails to get any bat on it.
Full and at the pads, Peter Handscomb uses his feet and turns it through square leg and retains the strike with a single.
Fuller and on off, Peter Handscomb presents a straight bat and defends it down the wicket.
Short and flatter outside off, Peter Handscomb goes back and pushes it back to the bowler.
Tossed up, fuller and outside off, Peter Handscomb uses his feet and smothers the ball down the wicket.
Loopy delivery, full around off, Peter Handscomb works it towards cover.
Full and quicker on off, Peter Handscomb clips but fails to get it past short mid-wicket.
Short and outside off, Peter Handscomb dabs this one towards backward point and keeps the strike for the next over with a single.
Full and around off, Peter Handscomb shapes to sweep but ends up pushing it back to the bowler.
Slower and full on off, Peter Handscomb gets forward and defends it down the wicket.

OUT! LBW! Ravindra Jadeja gets a five-wicket haul in his comeback from injury! He fires this one full and quicker at the stumps, Peter Handscomb gets across to sweep this one on the leg side but fails to get any bat on it. The ball catches him right in front of the stumps and the umpire raises his finger. Peter Handscomb goes upstairs for a review but the UltraEdge shows no bat involved. It is three reds on Ball Tracking and Peter Handscomb's vigil comes to an end. Australia have one wicket left and India will want to get this inning over as soon as possibe.
Full and outside off, Scott Boland strokes this one towards cover.
This is slightly short and in line with the stumps. Scott Boland goes deep in the crease and blocks this back down the pitch.
Full and outside off, Scott Boland pushes this one towards short cover. A half-stop there allows Scott Boland to open his account with a single.
Short and turning into the batter, Scott Boland goes back to defend but gets hit high on the pads.
Full and quicker on off, Scott Boland blocks this one out on the off side.
Fullish outside off, Scott Boland leans forward and smothers the ball on the off side.
Short and quicker outside off, Scott Boland pushes at the delivery but gets beaten on the outside edge.

OUT! BOWLED! Australia have been bowled out for 177! Ravichandran Ashwin bowls a carrom delivery and serves it full on off, Scott Boland fails to read the delivery and plays down the wrong line as he gets forward to defend. The ball goes past his outside edge and knocks the off stump back. Ravichandran Ashwin gets his third wicket to bring an end to the Australian innings.

FOUR! Rohit Sharma is off the mark with a boundary! Seems a bit lucky but he will take it gladly. Pat Cummins bowls this on a good length and outside off. Rohit Sharma looks to leave this but the ball goes from the toe end of the bat through the slip cordon for four runs to third man.
FOUR! No luck is needed for this! Pat Cummins bowls this full and on the pads. Rohit Sharma clips this towards deep mid-wicket and collects four more runs.
On a good length in the channel outside off, Rohit Sharma defends this one down the wicket.

FOUR! Easy pickings for Rohit Sharma! You can bowl all day on his legs and he will keep hitting it away. Pat Cummins bowls this full and Rohit Sharma flicks this towards deep mid-wicket for yet another boundary.
Strays down leg side once again and on a fuller length. Rohit Sharma clips this towards deep backward square leg for a single.

On a good length this time and just outside off. KL Rahul looks to play this leg side but the ball takes the leading edge and falls back down the pitch. Good start for India as 13 runs come from the first over.
Scott Boland begins with a full delivery outside the off stump. Rohit Sharma punches this to the right of mid off and they take a couple of runs as the fielder gives chase.
On a good length this time and angled into the stumps. Rohit Sharma tucks this towards square leg.
Continues to bowl on a good length and just outside the off pole. Rohit Sharma gets across to cover the line of the ball and blocks this one out.
Goes full once again and outside the off stump. Rohit Sharma gets his front foot forward and knocks this towards cover.
Angles this into the stumps from outside off. Rohit Sharma dabs this towards the mid on fielder.
Outside the off stump this time on a good length. Rohit Sharma stands tall and blocks this to the left of the bowler.
Pat Cummins gets the ball to nip back in sharply. This is bowled full and wide outside off. KL Rahul gets a good stride forward and leaves the ball alone.
On a good length this time and outside the of stump. KL Rahul defends this solidly towards cover.
On a good length this time and outside the off pole. KL Rahul stands tall and dabs it into the off side.
Continues to bowl on a good length. KL Rahul knocks this back to the bowler.
Bowls this full and just outside the off stump. KL Rahul gets forward and blocks this solidly.
Goes really full and into the stumps. KL Rahul digs this out towards mid on.
Nathan Lyon fires this one full and outside the off stump. Rohit Sharma is watchful and leaves this one alone.
Angles this into the pads on a shorter length. Rohit Sharma goes back and dabs this towards short leg.
Flighted full and outside the off pole. Rohit Sharma gets a good stride forward and blocks this into the off side.
Continues to bowl full and outside the off stump. Rohit Sharma knocks this towards point.
Loopy delivery bowled full and outside the off stump. Rohit Sharma sweeps this towards deep square leg for a single.
Bowls this quick and just outside off on a shorter length. KL Rahul rocks back and punches this back to the bowler.
Pat Cummins beats the outside edge! This is bowled on a good length and outside the off stump. Rohit Sharma pushes at this but does not connect and the ball stays low as well.
Delivers this on the pads on a fuller length. Rohit Sharma flicks this towards deep square leg and they take a couple of runs.

FOUR! Great use of the wrists! Pat Cummins is not getting his line right here as he bowls this on the pads on a fuller length. Rohit Sharma clips this towards deep square leg for four runs as the ball races across the turf.
On a good length and outside the off stump. Rohit Sharma blocks this towards cover.
Pat Cummins delivers this in line with the stumps. Rohit Sharma dabs this towards mid on.
FOUR! Another boundary for Rohit Sharma and he is off to a flier! Pat Cummins delivers this on the pads on a fuller length. Rohit Sharma glances this down to fine leg for four more runs.
Nathan Lyon bowls this full and wide outside the off stump. KL Rahul steps across and leaves this one alone.
Bowls this closer to the off pole. KL Rahul dabs this back towards the bowler.
Full and in line with the stumps. KL Rahul gets his bat down in time and taps it into the leg side.
Sightly short and outside the off stump. KL Rahul rocks back and knocks this to the right of the bowler.
Floats this one full and outside off. KL Rahul clips this towards mid on and sets off for a single.
Continues to bowl full and into the pads. Rohit Sharma pats this down towards short leg.
Scott Boland bowls this full and outside the off stump. KL Rahul gets forward and taps this towards cover.
On a good length and angling in form outside off. KL Rahul pushes this towards mid on.
Goes full and outside the off stump. KL Rahul taps this towards mid on.
Back to bowling on a good length and outside the off stump. KL Rahul leaves this one alone.
Scott Boland bowls this one full and on the pads. KL Rahul misses his flick and gets hit on the pads.
Continues bowling full and straight. KL Rahul eases this towards mid on. Maiden over from Scott Boland.
Nathan Lyon flights the full and outside the off stump. Rohit Sharma pushes this towards cover.
Short and in line with the stumps. Rohit Sharma dabs this towards short leg.
Floats this full and outside off. Rohit Sharma knocks this back towards the bowler.
Loopy delivery bowled on the pads. Rohit Sharma charges down the wicket and mistimes his shot towards deep square leg for a single.
Strays onto the pads on the fuller length. KL Rahul clips this down to deep backward square leg for a single.
FOUR! Sixth boundary for Rohit Sharma! Nathan Lyon floats this one full and outside the off stump. Rohit Sharma knocks this past the mid off fielder for four more runs.
Scott Boland bowls this on a good length and outside the off stump. KL Rahul blocks this towards cover.
On a good length and outside the off pole. KL Rahul pushes this into the off side.

Extra bit of bounce off the surface! Scott Boland bowls this on a good length and outside off. KL Rahul gets forward and gets deceived by the bounce. The ball goes off the outside edge towards third man for a couple of runs.
Angles this into the stumps on a good length. KL Rahul dabs this towards the mid on fielder.
Goes full and strays down leg. KL Rahul misses his flick and gets hit on the pads. A stifled appeal from the bowler but the umpire says no.
Back to bowling on a good length and outside off. KL Rahul knocks this back towards the bowler.
Nathan Lyon floats this full and in line with the stumps Rohit Sharma blocks this back towards the bowler.
Flighted full and just outside the off pole. Rohit Sharma gets forward and smothers this into the pitch.
Fires this one full and into the stumps. Rohit Sharma defends this solidly into the off side.
Gets this one to keep its line outside off on a fuller length. Rohit Sharma looks to play this leg side and gets a leading edge to short third man.
Bowls this short and going down leg. Rohit Sharma looks to glance this fine but misses.
Goes back to bowling full and outside the off stump. Rohit Sharma dead bats it back down the pitch towards the bowler.
Todd Murphy fires this one full and outside the off stump. KL Rahul dabs this into the off side.
Floats this one full and outside the off stump. KL Rahul pushes this through the point region for a single.
NO BALL! Loops this one full and outside the off stump. Rohit Sharma looks to defend and gets an inside edge on the pads. He oversteps though and it will be a no ball.
Flights this full and into the stumps. Rohit Sharma flicks this towards wide long on for a single.
Slightly short and angled into the pads. KL Rahul dabs this towards short leg.
Goes full this time and wider outside off. KL Rahul defends this towards cover.
Gets this closer to the off pole on a fuller length. KL Rahul taps this back down the pitch to the left of the bowler.
Nathan Lyon bowls this short and in line with the stumps. Rohit Sharma dabs this towards mid-wicket.
Bowls full this time and just outside the of stump. Rohit Sharma flicks this to the left of the mid-wicket fielder.
Flighted delivery bowled full and outside the off stump. Rohit Sharma shimmies down the wicket and defends this into the off side.
A tad bit shorter this time and on the pads. Rohit Sharma tucks this towards square leg.
Loopy delivery bowled full and on an off stump line. Rohit Sharma gets a good stride forward and keeps the ball out.
Slightly short and in line with the stumps. Rohit Sharma dabs this down to the short-leg fielder.
Todd Murphy floats this one full and just outside the off pole. KL Rahul taps this into the leg side.

Flights this one full and in line with the stumps. KL Rahul gets a good stride forward and looks to defend the ball but misses and gets hit on the pads. A huge appeal from the bowler but they do not review this/
Loopy delivery in line with the stumps. KL Rahul defends this back down the pitch.
Flighted full and outside the off stump. KL Rahul blocks this to the off side.
Floats the one full outside off KL Rahul blocks this out solidly.
Fires this one full and into the pads. KL Rahul clips this to deep square leg for a single.
Short and quicker on middle from 'round the wicket, KL Rahul defends it on the back foot.
Short and flatter on off, KL Rahul hangs back and punches it down to long on for a single.
Lyon pushes this one full and quicker outside off, Rohit Sharma leans forward to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Was that a chance? Short and at the batter, Rohit Sharma steps out to defend but fends this one towards short leg. Marnus Labuschagne there fails to hang onto it.
Flighted, full at the stumps, Rohit Sharma smothers the ball down the wicket.
SIX! Rohit Sharma goes huge! Nathan Lyon floats this one, full and on middle, Rohit Sharma shimmies down the track and thumps it down the ground towards long off for a maximum.
Short and on off, KL Rahul goes back in his crease and punches it towards covers for a couple of runs.
Fires this one full and quicker on off, KL Rahul tries to defend from the crease but gets an outside edge that goes on the bounce towards first slip.
Floats this full and outside off. KL Rahul defends this into the off side.
Slower and short on off, KL Rahul stays on the back foot and works it towards deep mid-wicket for a single.
Short and at the pads, Rohit Sharma tries to turn this one on the leg side but gets hit on the thigh pad.
Tossed up, full on middle and leg, Rohit Sharma taps it to short leg.
Short and quicker at the stumps, KL Rahul defends this one from the back foot.
Tossed up, full at the stumps, KL Rahul uses his feet and flicks it straight to mid-wicket.
Short and on middle and leg, KL Rahul rocks back in his crease and works it wide of mid-wicket for a single. 50-run stand comes up.
FOUR! Nathan Lyon overpitches this one outside off, Rohit Sharma picks the length early and gets it through the vacant covers region for a boundary.
Short and flatter on middle, Rohit Sharma gets behind and blocks it on the off side.
Short and angling away on middle, Rohit Sharma stays on the back foot and defends it towards short leg.
Short and flatter on middle from 'round the wicket, KL Rahul goes on the back foot and pushes it to mid-wicket.
Flighted, full and on middle, KL Rahul gets forward to defend but gets an inside edge that rolls towards short fine leg. Rohit Sharma wants a single but gets sent back.
Fuller on middle, KL Rahul leans forward and defends it to short leg.
Slower and full on middle, KL Rahul blocks this one out down the wicket.
Another full delivery at the stumps, KL Rahul pushes this one to the right of the bowler.
Fuller and on middle and leg, KL Rahul gets forward and clips this one wide of mid-wicket for a single.
Cummins bowls this one full and outside off, KL Rahul drives it firmly but straight to mid off.
Another full delivery outside off, KL Rahul gets behind the line and pushes it to cover.
FOUR! Nicely played! Pat Cummins bowls this one full and outside off, KL Rahul leans forward and drives it through covers for a boundary.
On a good length on off, KL Rahul knocks this one to mid off for a dot.
Fullish delivery on off, KL Rahul drives it with a straight bat but Pat Cummins stops it with his left hand.
Back of a length and angling down the leg side, KL Rahul leaves the ball alone.
Bowls this one full and outside off, Rohit Sharma presses forward and defends it on the off side.
Full and quicker outside off, Rohit Sharma uses his feet and pushes it back to the bowler.
Full and at the stumps, Rohit Sharma pushes this one to the left of mid-wicket.
Full and on off, Rohit Sharma advances and knocks it back to the bowler.
Fullish delivery on middle, Rohit Sharma tries to turn this one towards mid-wicket but closes the bat face early. Mishits it to cover for a single.
Short and at the pads, KL Rahul looks to work it on the leg side but fails to get any bat on it.
Full and angling away on off, Rohit Sharma gets forward and blocks this one out.
Flighted, full and on middle and leg, Rohit Sharma works this one to short leg.
Slower and full at the stumps, Rohit Sharma uses his feet and pushes it wide of short leg.
Short and down the leg side, Rohit Sharma shapes to pull but the ball keeps very low and he fails to connect. Alex Carey behind the wicket dives to his left and collects it cleanly.
Floated, full around off, Rohit Sharma takes a stride forward and defends it down the wicket.
Full and quicker on off, Rohit Sharma stays in the crease and tries to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Tossed up, full and on middle, KL Rahul gets forward and defends it to short leg.
Full and at the stumps, KL Rahul defends this one form the front foot.
Flighted, full on middle, KL Rahul uses his feet and knocks it down to long on for a single.
Full and on middle by Todd Murphy, Rohit Sharma advances and pushes it back to the bowler.
Floated, full at the pads, Rohit Sharma uses his feet and clips it to deep mid-wicket for a single.
Full and flatter on middle, KL Rahul leans forward and defends it down the wicket.
Flighted, full around off, Rohit Sharma drives this one through the vacant covers region. Pat Cummins performs the chase and saves a run for his side.
Full and on off, KL Rahul works this one from the front foot to mid-wicket.
Lyon switches to over the wicket and bowls it short and turning into the batter, KL Rahul hangs back and punches it to mid-wicket.
Short and quicker at the stumps, the ball keeps a bit low but KL Rahul still manages to push this one down to long on for a single.

FOUR! FIFTY for Rohit Sharma! Nathan Lyon tosses this one full and on off, Rohit Sharma gets into the position early and paddles this one towards the fine leg region. Gets it to the right of short fine leg and collects a boundary to bring up his fifty.

FOUR! Back-to-back boundaries for Rohit Sharma! Nathan Lyon overpitches and bowls this one full and outside off, Rohit Sharma does not miss out and drives it firmly through the covers region for yet another boundary.
Short and at the pads, KL Rahul goes back in his crease and punches it wide of deep mid-wicket for a couple of runs.
Full and on off by Todd Murphy, KL Rahul leans forward and smothers the ball on the off side.
Full and quicker outside off, KL Rahul defends it from the front foot.
Flighted, full on off, KL Rahul gets forward and defends it on the off side.

OUT! CAUGHT AND BOWLED! Todd Murphy gets his first wicket in Test cricket! Todd Murphy tosses this one full and around off, KL Rahul goes for the drive on the off side and plays it a bit early. The ball takes the inner part of the bat and lobs it back to the bowler. Todd Murphy makes no mistake and he is chuffed to bits. Australia will be relieved to break this partnership.
Full and quicker at the stumps, Ravichandran Ashwin gets forward and defends it back to the bowler.

A loud appeal but turned down! Nathan Lyon bowls this one full and quicker on off, Rohit Sharma leans forward to defend but gets rapped on the front pad. Australia go up in appeal but it is turned down by the umpire. They think of a review but decide against it.
Fuller at the stumps, Rohit Sharma drives this one down to long on for a single.
Short and turning into the pads, Ravichandran Ashwin goes back in his crease and works it to short leg.
Lyon persists with full length and bowls it on middle, Ravichandran Ashwin smothers the ball on the off side.
Full and quicker on off, Ravichandran Ashwin takes a big stride forward and blocks this one out.
Full and on middle, Ravichandran Ashwin gets forward and defends it down the wicket. That will be STUMPS on Day 1!
Murphy starts with a short delivery at the stumps, Rohit Sharma hangs back and defends it back to the bowler.
Rohit Sharma and India are underway on Day 2! Tossed up, full and on middle, Rohit Sharma steps out and pushes it down to long on for a single.
Pushed straight, full and around off, Ravichandran Ashwin presses forward but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Flatter and quicker on middle, Ravichandran Ashwin defends this one from the crease to short leg.
Full and quicker on middle, Ravichandran Ashwin goes back and blocks this one out.
Flighted delivery, full on middle, Ravichandran Ashwin gets behind the line and smothers the ball down the wicket.
Starts with a full delivery outside off, Rohit Sharma pushes this one wide of deep point and collects a couple of runs.
Shorter in length, outside off, Rohit Sharma hangs back and works it to mid-wicket.
On a good length angling in on off, Rohit Sharma blocks this one out on the off side.
Another one on a good length outside off, Rohit Sharma taps it towards point and wants a single. But eventually sends Ravichandran Ashwin back just in time.
Beaten! Good-length delivery in the channel outside off, Rohit Sharma stays inside the line and tries to defend but gets beaten on the outside edge.
Full around off by Pat Cummins, Rohit Sharma pushes this one to cover.

FOUR! Nathan Lyon gets the outside edge straight away! Floats this one full and allows the ball to keep its line outside off. Ravichandran Ashwin looks to push it away but gets an edge towards third man for four runs.
Bowls full and outside the off stump. Ravichandran Ashwin dabs this to the left of the bowler.
Flights this one full and in line with the stumps. Ravichandran Ashwin pushes at this and gets an inside edge to short fine leg.
Huge appeal! This is full and spinning down leg from the middle stump. Ravichandran Ashwin misses his block and gets hit on the pads. The umpire remains unmoved.
Loopy delivery bowled full and straight. Ravichandran Ashwin blocks this back down the pitch towards  the bowler.
Tosses this one full and outside the off pole. Ravichandran Ashwin gets a good stride forward and drives this to deep cover for a couple of runs.
Pat Cummins bowls this slightly back of a length and outside the off stump. Rohit Sharma dabs this into the point region and takes a single.

FOUR! More runs for India as Pat Cummins continues to concede runs! This is bowled full and angled in from outside the off stump. Ravichandran Ashwin hits a controlled stroke towards deep backward point for four runs.
This is on a good length and outside the off pole. Ravichandran Ashwin turns this towards the backward point fielder.
Gets this one to nip back in from just outside the off stump in a good length. Ravichandran Ashwin misses his shot and gets hit on the pads.

Oh my! That ball has stayed really low. Pat Cummins serves this on a good length and outside off. Ravichandran Ashwin looks to play at it but misses with the ball going way under his bat to the keeper.
Bowls this in line with the stumps on a good length. Ravichandran Ashwin eases this towards mid on.
Nathan Lyon flights this full and on an off-stump line. Rohit Sharma dabs this to the right of the bowler.
Floats this one full and straight. Rohit Sharma shimmies down the wicket and clips this down to long on for one.
Bowls this slightly short and at the stumps. Ravichandran Ashwin rocks back in the crease and tucks this towards mid-wicket.
Beaten! Gets the ball to skid through outside off on a fuller length. Ravichandran Ashwin pushes at this but does not connect.
Loopy delivery bowled wider outside off. Ravichandran Ashwin strokes this throough covers and collects two runs.
Gets this one to spin down leg side on a shorter length. Ravichandran Ashwin looks to flick this fine but misses.
Pat Cummins bowls this on a fuller length and just outside the off pole. Rohit Sharma leans forward and blocks this solidly towards mid on.
Delivers this on a fuller length as well and in line with the stumps. Rohit Sharma flicks this towards the mid-wicket fielder.
Bowls this one on a good length and angles this in from just outside off. Rohit Sharma tucks this towards mid-wicket.
Goes back to bowling full and outside the off pole. Rohit Sharma gets behind the line of the ball and defends this towards mid on.
Outside the off stump on a fuller length. Rohit Sharma dabs this towards point with soft hands.
A rare maiden over from Australia! This is bowled on a good length and outside off. Rohit Sharma is watchful as he blocks the ball into the off side.
Nathan Lyon bowls this short and in line with the stumps. Ravichandran Ashwin goes on the back foot and blocks this towards the bowler.
Goes full and into the pads. Ravichandran Ashwin clears his front foot and digs this back towards Nathan Lyon.
Flights this full and straight. Ravichandran Ashwin dabs this back down the pitch.
Continues to bowl full and outside the leg stump. Ravichandran Ashwin pushes this to the right of the bowler.

Flights this one full and just outside the off stump. Ravichandran Ashwin pushes at this and gets an outside edge towards point. Rohit Sharma calls him through for a single but Ravichandran Ashwin is late to respond. Makes it across in time.
Loops this one full and spinning down leg from middle. Rohit Sharma looks to lean forward and gets beaten by the turn to get hit on the pads.
Pat Cummins bowls this on a good length but strays onto the pads. Ravichandran Ashwin clips this straight to the square leg fielder.
Continues to bowl on a good length and just outside the off pole. Ravichandran Ashwin gets across the stumps and defends this to mid on.
Delivers this outside the off pole on a good length. Ravichandran Ashwin looks to drive on the up but miscues his shot back towards the bowler.
Bowls this one slightly back of a length and going down leg. Ravichandran Ashwin is watchful as he raises his arms and lets the keeper collect the ball.
Goes full and outside the off pole. Ravichandran Ashwin looks to go for the expansive drive and miscues his shot wide of mid on. They rush across for a single.

SIX! Just over the fielder! Pat Cummins bangs this in short and outside the off stump. Rohit Sharma gets into position in a flash and pulls this over the deep square leg fielder for a maximum. This shot came out of nowhere and is also been Rohit Sharma's kryptonite in the past. Executes it well this time though. This six brings up the 100 for India.
Nathan Lyon goes over the wicket and floats this one full and outside the off stump. Ravichandran Ashwin blocks this out in the off side.

SIX! That sounded meaty as soon as Ravichandran Ashwin made contact with the ball! Nathan Lyon flights this full and outside the off stump. Ravichandran Ashwin gets on his knees and slog sweeps this over deep mid-wicket for a maximum.
Tosses this full and outside the off pole. Ravichandran Ashwin pushes this into the off side.
Floats this one full and into the pads. Ravichandran Ashwin clips this towards deep square leg for a single.
Bowls this slightly short and in line with the stumps from 'round the wicket. Rohit Sharma sits in the crease and blocks this one out.
Loopy delivery bowled full and on a leg stump line. Rohit Sharma eases this down to long on for one and will keep strike.

Scott Boland starts off with a good-length delivery that nips back in sharply from just outside off. Rohit Sharma looks to clip this leg side but gets cramped for room and gets hit on the pads. A stifled appeal by the bowler but nothing comes from it. They take a leg bye as the ball rolls towards backward point.
Bowls this one full and outside the off stump. Ravichandran Ashwin blocks this towards cover.
On a good length this time and outside off. Ravichandran Ashwin taps this towards mid on.
Slightly fuller and angles into the stumps on a good length. Ravichandran Ashwin clips this towards mid-wicket.
Goes full and outside off. Ravichandran Ashwin pushes  this towards mid off.
Bowls this one full and on off, Ravichandran Ashwin gets on the front foot and drives it back to the bowler.
Nathan Lyon loops this one full and in line with the stumps. Rohit Sharma gets forward and dabs this into the leg side.
Flighted full and outside the off stump. Rohit Sharma shimmies down the wicket and pushes this towards mid off.
Tosses this one full and straight. Rohit Sharma taps this down towards short leg.
Continues to bowl full and on a leg stump line. Rohit Sharma looks to get forward but ends up clipping this towards mid-wicket.
Flighted delivery once again bowled outside off. Rohit Sharma down the wicket once more but defends this into the off side.
FOUR! A bit of luck going India's way as well! Nathan Lyon loops this full and outside off. Rohit Sharma looks to work this leg side but gets a leading edge down to thrid man for four runs.
Scott Boland bowls this on a good length and outside the off stump. Ravichandran Ashwin knocks this on the up towards the cover fielder.
Continues to bowl on a good length and outside the off stump. Ravichandran Ashwin pushes this towards mid off.
Gets this one to shape back in from outside off and serves this slightly short. Ravichandran Ashwin stands tall and looks to punch this away bit does not time it well.
On a good length once again and outside off. Ravichandran Ashwin gets an inside edge into the leg side.
Goes slightly fuller this time and outside off. Ravichandran Ashwin knocks this to the mid off fielder.
Two maidens in a row for Scott Boland in this spell. Continues to bowl on a good length and on the outside off-stump channel. Ravichandran Ashwin defends this back towards the bowler.
Nathan Lyon bowls this full and outside off. Rohit Sharma stays deep in the crease and blocks this into the off side.
Flights this one full and on the pads. Rohit Sharma clips this to deep backward square leg and takes a single.
Loopy delivery bowled full and outside off. Ravichandran Ashwin gets well forward and gets the off the outside half of his bat towards point for a quick single.
Tosses this one full and outside the off stump. Rohit Sharma blocks this slightly uppishly back towards the bowler.
Continues to flight and bowls it full, in line with the stumps. Rohit Sharma well forward to dabs this back down the pitch.
Loops this one full and into the pads. Rohit Sharma clips this towards the fielder at short mid-wicket. This partnership is building nicely for India.
Scott Boland bowls this on a good length and just outside off. Ravichandran Ashwin dabs this towards mid-wicket.
Bowls this on a good length as well and outside off with the wicket-keeper standing at the stumps. Ravichandran Ashwin blocks this solidly towards cover.
